g.text: Guest feels hungry and reviews menu
RSM assigns order to a Room Service Waiter
Waiter debits guest's account for the order
Waiter prepares service cart and any non-alcoholic drinks
Waiter delivers the complete order to the guest's room
RSM coordinates with Kitchen Staff (drops off order ticket)
Kitchen Staff prepares food items and places on pick-up counter
Guest places order to Room Service Manager
RSM coordinates with Sommelier (if alcoholic beverages ordered)
Sommelier selects wine or prepares alcoholic drinks
Waiter picks up prepared food from kitchen's pick-up counter
Guest enjoys meal and decides whether to leave a tip
Waiter collects alcoholic beverages from Sommelier
